gobblin.recordaccess

Class AvroGenericRecordAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.recordaccess.AvroGenericRecordAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecordAccessor

    public class AvroGenericRecordAccessor
extends Object
implements RecordAccessor
    Implementation of a RecordAccessor that can process Avro GenericRecords. NOTE: This class assumes field names never contain a '.'; it assumes they are always nested.
